## =========================================

## CORE LOOP (FINAL SYSTEM)

## =========================================

while True:

```
perceive()                  # later connects to robot
event = build_event()
memory.store(event)

update_internal_state()

if no_goal:
    goals = generate_goals()
    goal = select_goal(goals)

plan = create_plan(goal)
execute(plan)

feedback = evaluate()
apply_feedback()

if time_to_reflect:
    reflect()
```

